name: Tumpinamba Comic Book
description:
Read the book...
Who was I to choose , Who was I , Who was I to lose. Life told me many worlds and many visions. All I had to do was live to really see it. Seeing that the truth believed is more than meaning. Everything that i could see i did perceive it. Everything that we must be , i couldnt leave it. Love left by the side. But our eyes bring. A storm is brewing inside myself....... A heart is here... But all we said, we had to fall... But I walked ...away..... From it... Life was reborn and all i could have felt. Was faded by the storm...again....the best of us ...the rest of us. 

This life is more than eye, could see you there. I felt as though i had fallen, from the ends of time. I truely held myself apart. From eternity. From the best of me. I could not beleive. In an an ordinary way of being. In an ordinary way .To see the truth. Behold my friends Strong images of new visions. New defusions, and new infunsions. There Once was a hero...
He was built by design....

Created 2017-2020
40+ Page Full Color Trippy Comic Book
all holders will be entered in receiving a full print out of the book with 3d glasses. this book acts as a whitelist for the upcoming collection of one off pages. as well as the follow up Tumpinamba Remix Gif/Video Comic Book Opera....
